      "q15_540301": "My parents ask me what I think before most family decisions affecting me are made.",
      "q15_540301_opt_1": "NO!",
      "q15_540301_opt_2": "no",
      "q15_540301_opt_3": "yes",
      "q15_540301_opt_4": "YES!",
      "frequency_parents_proud": "How often do your parents tell you they're proud of you for something you've done?",
